  EffectDiscription_ENG: '[Start of Your Main Phase] For the turn, when this Digimon
    would digivolve into a card with [Tyrannomon] in its name, or the [Dinosaur]
    or [Ceratopsian] trait, reduce the digivolution cost by 1.'
